# Contribution Module ‚Äî Governance Rules

## Merge Rules

- Must be linked to an issue or proposal
- CI must pass
- Required reviews must be completed
- Audit impact must be declared

## Proposal Lifecycle

1. Draft opened
2. Reviewed by Steward or Maintainer
3. Approved and tagged
4. Implemented via PR
5. Merged with audit trace

## Bounty Rules

- Must be declared in issue or proposal
- Claimed by contributor
- Verified by review
- Paid via value-flow module
